-We're family?
-Mm-hmm.

1:16:28.839 --> 1:16:30.339
Do you know what that feels like?

1:16:31.633 --> 1:16:33.843
Yes, I know what that feels like.

1:16:34.845 --> 1:16:36.355
Aw!

1:16:36.513 --> 1:16:39.853
Hey! Hey, come on. Out of the truck.
