1:25:55.739 --> 1:25:59.159
-Yes.
-Absolutely! Go get them, kelpcake.

1:26:04.706 --> 1:26:06.916
Yeah. I did it.

1:26:09.920 --> 1:26:12.550
-Hmm.
-Hmm.

1:26:17.845 --> 1:26:19.725
